  "purpose": "Generate MCP ( Model Context Protocol ) server implementations \n from concept projections Owns tool resource template \n classification , input schema derivation , description \n generation for LLM comprehension , transport setup \n ( stdio , SSE , HTTP ) , and hierarchical tool grouping When \n @ hierarchical trait is present , generates path based resource \n URIs and list children get ancestors tool variants \n Enrichment content from Projection is passed through for \n tool description enhancement \n See Architecture doc Section 2.5"
